<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#1fc0fd5615cf394b5628dc4a427a0ce0>.
<#1fc0fd5615cf394b5628dc4a427a0ce0> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/CONSIL_PRES>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T17:12:12.185Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#1fc0fd5615cf394b5628dc4a427a0ce0> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/CONSIL_PRES> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "false";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#exactMatch> <http://eurovoc.europa.eu/5806>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Președinția Consiliului UE"@ro, "Uachtaránacht Chomhairle an AE"@ga, "Predsjedništvo Vijeća EU-a"@hr, "Presidência do Conselho da UE"@pt, "Il-Presidenza tal-Kunsill tal-UE"@mt, "Prezydencja w Radzie UE"@pl, "ELi nõukogu eesistujariik"@et, "Presidencia del Consejo de la UE"@es, "Predsedstvo Sveta EU"@sl, "Formandskabet for EU-Rådet"@da, "Présidence du Conseil de l’UE"@fr, "ES Tarybai pirmininkaujanti valstybė narė"@lt, "EU:n neuvoston puheenjohtajuus"@fi, "Az EU Tanácsának elnöksége"@hu, "Presidenza del Consiglio dell’UE"@it, "ES Padomes prezidentūra"@lv, "Predsedníctvo Rady EÚ"@sk, "Vorsitz des Rates der EU"@de, "Προεδρία του Συμβουλίου της ΕΕ"@el, "Předsednictví Rady EU"@cs, "Voorzitterschap van de Raad van de EU"@nl, "Председателство на Съвета на ЕС"@bg, "EU-rådets ordförandeskap"@sv, "Presidency of the Council of the EU"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The presidency of the Council of the EU rotates among the European Union member states every six months. During this six-month period, the presidency chairs meetings at every level in the Council, helping to ensure the continuity of the EU’s work in the Council. Member states holding the presidency work together closely in groups of three, called ‘trios’. The trio sets long-term goals and prepares a common agenda determining the topics and major issues that will be addressed by the Council over an 18-month period."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "CONSIL_PRES"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001486"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "CONSIL_PRES"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Az Európai Unió Tanácsának elnöksége"@hu, "Europos Sąjungos Tarybai pirmininkaujanti valstybė narė"@lt, "Prezidentūra Eiropas Savienības Padomē"@lv, "Prezydencja Rady Unii Europejskiej"@pl, "Euroopan unionin neuvoston puheenjohtajuus"@fi, "Predsjedništvo Vijeća Europske unije"@hr, "Președinția Consiliului Uniunii Europene"@ro, "Προεδρία του Συμβουλίου της Ευρωπαϊκής Ένωσης"@el, "Formandskabet for Rådet for Den Europæiske Union"@da, "Voorzitterschap van de Raad van de Europese Unie"@nl, "Presidência do Conselho da União Europeia"@pt, "Předsednictví Rady Evropské unie"@cs, "Presidencia del Consejo de la Unión Europea"@es, "Vorsitz des Rates der Europäischen Union"@de, "Predsedstvo Sveta Evropske unije"@sl, "Presidency of the Council of the European Union"@en, "Presidenza del Consiglio dell’Unione europea"@it, "Euroopa Liidu Nõukogu eesistuja"@et, "Uachtaránacht Chomhairle an Aontais Eorpaigh"@ga, "Il-Presidenza tal-Kunsill tal-Unjoni Ewropea"@mt, "Présidence du Conseil de l’Union européenne"@fr, "Ordförandeskapet för Europeiska unionens råd"@sv, "Predsedníctvo Rady Európskej únie"@sk, "Председателство на Съвета на Европейския съюз"@bg;
